---
layout: base.njk
title: Blog - Tommy Roy
---

<div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row mb-5 text-center">
        <div class="col-12">
            <h1 class="display-4 praise-font" style="color: #341830;">Journal de Bord</h1>
            <p class="lead text-muted">Réflexions sur la physique, la peinture et le code.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
            <div class="list-group shadow-sm">
                
                {% for post in collections.blogPosts %}
                    <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="list-group-item list-group-item-action p-4 border-0 border-bottom">
                        <div class="d-flex w-100 justify-content-between align-items-center mb-2">
                            <h2 class="h4 mb-0" style="color: #341830;">{{ post.data.title }}</h2>
                            <small class="text-muted text-nowrap ms-3">
                                {{ post.date | readableDate }}
                            </small>
                        </div>
                        
                        <p class="mb-1 text-secondary">
                            {% if post.data.description %}
                                {{ post.data.description }}
                            {% else %}
                                Lire l'article...
                            {% endif %}
                        </p>
                        
                        <div class="mt-2">
                            {% for tag in post.data.tags %}
                                {% if tag != "posts" %}
                                    <span class="badge bg-light text-dark border">{{ tag }}</span>
                                {% endif %}
                            {% endfor %}
                        </div>
                    </a>
                {% else %}
                    <div class="p-4 text-center text-muted">
                        <p>Aucun article publié pour le moment.</p>
                    </div>
                {% endfor %}
                
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
     <div class="row mb-5 text-center" style="min-height: 300px">
               <iframe src="https://tommyroy.substack.com/embed" width="480" height="150" frameborder="0" scrolling="no"></iframe> 
    </div>
</div>